## Bid Management Workflow

- [ ] 1. Audit current bids: Review current CPC/bid levels vs. performance
- [ ] 2. Set objectives: Define target CPA, ROAS, or volume goals
- [ ] 3. Choose strategy: Select manual CPC, Target CPA, Target ROAS, Maximize Conversions
- [ ] 4. Segment by performance: Identify top-performing and underperforming keywords/audiences
- [ ] 5. Adjust bids: Raise bids on high performers, lower or pause low performers
- [ ] 6. Monitor pacing: Ensure spend is on track to hit daily/monthly targets
- [ ] 7. Iterate: Refine bids based on early performance signals

## Key Inputs
- Campaign: {{campaign_name}}
- Platform: {{platform}}
- Target CPA: {{target_cpa}}
- Target ROAS: {{target_roas}}
- Budget: {{budget}}
